holder voting this year</a> =E2=80=94 on routine matters like electing dire=
ctors and approving executive pay =E2=80=94 only about 145 million shares (=
out of 516 million) were actually voted. So it might just be impossible for=
 AMC to get a majority of its shares to vote for <em>anything</em>.</p></bl=
ockquote>
