<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The resolution imposes broad limits on the pen=
sion fund=E2=80=99s investments. State administrators will be instructed to=
 prioritize =E2=80=9Cthe highest return on investment for beneficiaries, wi=
thout consideration for nonpecuniary beliefs or political factors.=E2=80=9D=
</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You can read <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/28834876.258574/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZmxnb3YuY29tL3dwLWN=
vbnRlbnQvdXBsb2Fkcy8yMDIyLzA4L0VTRy1SZXNvbHV0aW9uLUZpbmFsLnBkZg/607f07ceef4=
