et=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bo=
rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;"> the resolution</a> here; it objects to ESG=
 =E2=80=9Cprinciples,=E2=80=9D and says:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The evaluation by the Board of an investment d=
ecision must be based only on pecuniary factors. As used in this section, =
=E2=80=9Cpecuniary factor=E2=80=9D means a factor that the board prudently =
determines is expected to have a material effect on the risk and return of =
an investment based on appropriate investment horizons consistent with the =
fund=E2=80=99s investment objectives and funding policy. Pecuniary factors =
do not include the consideration of the furtherance of social, political, o=
r ideological interests.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The board may not subordinate the interests of=
 the participants and beneficiaries to other objectives and may not sacrifi=
ce investment return or take on additional investment risk to promote any n=
on-pecuniary factors. The weight given to any pecuniary factor by the board=
 should appropriately reflect a prudent assessment of its impact on risk an=
d returns.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well. If you are an ESG purist, you will say t=
hat there are no such things as =E2=80=9CESG principles.=E2=80=9D There are=
 ESG=C2=A0<em>risk factors</em>. The principle=C2=A0of Approach-2, ESG-puri=
st investing is =E2=80=9Cmake as much money as possible, by considering env=
ironmental, social and governance risk factors in your investment decisions=
.=E2=80=9D The only things that ESG purist investors consider are =E2=80=9C=
pecuniary factors,=E2=80=9D and they weigh them based on their prudent asse=
ssments of their impact on risk and returns over appropriate investment hor=
izons.=C2=A0 It=E2=80=99s just that they think that climate transition risk=
 is a big pecuniary factor. We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/28834876.258574/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2=
