 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;"> the letter</a> that Larry Fink, the chief executive officer =
of BlackRock Inc., sent to corporate CEOs in 2020. =E2=80=9CA Fundamental R=
eshaping of Finance,=E2=80=9D is the headline, and it says things like =E2=
=80=9CEvery government, company, and shareholder must confront climate chan=
ge=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9CBlackRock announced a number of initiatives to pla=
ce sustainability at the center of our investment approach.=E2=80=9D It is =
perhaps the high water mark of robust ESG rhetoric from asset managers; sin=
ce then, Republican opposition has gotten bolder and Fink has gotten more t=
imid. (His <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2883487=
6.258574/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxhY2tyb2NrLmNvbS91cy9pbmRpdmlkdWFsLzIwMjItbGFycn=
ktZmluay1jZW8tbGV0dGVy/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB56b0ccfa" itemprop=3D"Story=
