xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> letter t=
his year</a> says things like =E2=80=9CWe focus on sustainability not becau=
se we=E2=80=99re environmentalists, but because we are capitalists and fidu=
ciaries to our clients,=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9CStakeholder capitalism is not=
 about politics. It is not a social or ideological agenda. It is not =E2=80=
=98woke.=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D) But even that 2020 letter=C2=A0is really about =
financial risk and long-term profitability:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Because capital markets pull future risk forwa=
rd, we will see changes in capital allocation more quickly than we see chan=
ges to the climate itself. In the near future =E2=80=93 and sooner than mos=
t anticipate =E2=80=93 there will be a significant reallocation of capital.=
</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As a fiduciary, our responsibility is to help =
clients navigate this transition. Our investment conviction is that sustain=
ability- and climate-integrated portfolios can provide better risk-adjusted=
 returns to investors. And with the impact of sustainability on investment =
returns increasing, we believe that sustainable investing is the strongest =
foundation for client portfolios going forward.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Just pecuniary factors.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But I suspect that Ron DeSantis suspects that =
lots of ESG investors are=C2=A0<em>not=C2=A0</em>purists, that they have hy=
brid motives, that they are not=C2=A0<em>only=C2=A0</em>concerned with fina=
ncial risk but also have substantive environmental and social goals. And so=
 he confuses the issue too.=C2=A0=E2=80=9CGovernor Ron DeSantis Eliminates =
ESG Considerations from State Pension Investments,=E2=80=9D is the headline=
 on his <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28834876.2=
58574/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZmxnb3YuY29tLzIwMjIvMDgvMjMvZ292ZXJub3Itcm9uLWRlc2Fud=
