<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Three Danish pension fund clients of Federated=
 Hermes are demanding to know why it agreed to act as a gold sponsor for th=
e State Financial Officers Foundation =E2=80=94 a Republican group which ha=
s threatened to remove state pension assets from financial companies that d=
o not support fossil fuel industries. =E2=80=A6<br /><br />The clash highli=
ghts a tension between approaches to environmental, social and governance s=
tandards on both sides of the Atlantic. Support for stricter ESG standards =
across the corporate sector has been much stronger among investors based in=
