spread among Republican party supporters.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I guess the thinking=C2=A0is =E2=80=9Cdo ESG=
=C2=A0investing, but give money to Republican state financial officers so t=
hey leave you alone=E2=80=9D? Just exhausting.</p>
